Nice one. Two small suggestions:
- In your statement you discuss t first and then s - it helps if then in the input it is also t first and then s;
- 'They have the option to take a break' is confusing: suggestion to rephrase to 'They take a break of t minutes during the race'. (yes, maybe it is a break of 0 minutes ergo no break, but still they will take that one, it's not optional)
